uct e-learning from 14 to 21 February as a precaution after one of the cases involved a professor.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Kurohi |first1=Rei |last2=Baharudin |first2=Hariz |title=Coronavirus: 8 new cases in Singapore, including 5 more linked to Grace Assembly church, 1 linked to DBS case |url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/health/coronavirus-8-new-cases-in-singapore-including-5-more-linked-to-grace-assembly |website=The Straits Times |accessdate=13 February 2020 |date=13 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n* Unites States of America, the CDC confirmed the 15th US coronavirus case, a Wuhan evacuee quarantined at a military base in [[Texas]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/02/13/cdc-confirms-15th-us-case-of-coronavirus-among-wuhan-evacuees-under-quarantine-at-texas-military-base.html|title=CDC confirms 15th US coronavirus case, a Wuhan evacuee quarantined at Texas military base|first=William|last=Feuer|date=13 February 2020|website=CNBC}}</ref>\n\n* The Chinese government has issued extension of order to shut down all non-essential companies, including manufacturing plants, in Hubei Province until at least 24:00 20 February 2020.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1658402162460563869 |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:\u6e56\u5317\u7ee7\u7eed\u5ef6\u8fdf\u590d\u5de5\u5f00\u5b66\uff1a\u4f01\u4e1a\u4e0d\u65e9\u4e8e2\u670820\u65e524\u65f6\u524d\u590d\u5de5|date=13 February 2020 |website=baijiahao.baidu.com |publisher=Hubei Provincial New Coronavirus Infectious Pneumonia Prevention and Control Headquarters |access-date=17 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n====Discrepancy in the number of cases====\n\nThe same day, Hubei reported newly confirmed cases of 14,840, nearly 10 times more than the previous day, while deaths more than doubled to 242. This was due to the change in definition that included clinical (radiological) diagnosis of patients.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.scmp.com/news/china/society/article/3050354/coronavirus-hubei-province-reports-sharp-spike-new-confirmed|title=Hubei's coronavirus cases rise 10-fold after change in diagnostic criteria|date=13 February 2020|website=South China Morning Post|language=en|access-date=13 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/number-of-dead-from-coronavirus-surges-as-china-changes-way-it-counts-cases-2179409|title=Number Of Dead From Virus Surges As China Changes Way It Counts Cases|website=NDTV.com|access-date=13 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/02/13/coronavirus-latest-updates-china-hubei.html|title=Coronavirus live updates: China's Hubei reports 14,840 new cases, 242 additional deaths|last=Tan|first=Weizhen|date=12 February 2020|website=CNBC|language=en|access-date=13 February 2020}}</ref> The World Health Organization indicated that for consistency it would report only the number of laboratory-confirmed  cases.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.who.int/docs/default-source/coronaviruse/situation-reports/20200213-sitrep-24-covid-19.pdf|title=Coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19)Situation Report \u201324|website=who.int|access-date=14 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n=== 14 February ===\n\n'''WHO''' Situation Report 25:<ref>{{cite web|title=Novel Coronavirus (COVID-19) Situation Report \u2013 25 |url=https://www.who.int/docs/default-source/coronaviruse/situation-reports/20200214-sitrep-25-covid-19.pdf?sfvrsn=61dda7d_2 |website=[[World Health Organization|WHO]] |date=14 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n* Canada confirmed [[British Columbia]]'s fifth presumptive case, bringing the total number in the country to 8.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Campbell |first1=Alan |title=Coronavirus update: 5th case revealed in B.C. |url=https://www.richmond-news.com/news/coronavirus-update-5th-case-revealed-in-b-c-1.24076695 |website=Richmond News |accessdate=14 February 2020 |date=14 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n* Egypt confirmed its first case, a foreigner of undisclosed nationality. This was the first case on the African continent.<ref>{{Cite web|