nImport duties and US-specific tariffs were exempted on imported materials donated for epidemic prevention and control, including VAT and sales tax; the duties and tariffs previously levied were to be refunded.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3932987.html |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:\u4e09\u90e8\u95e8\uff1a\u5bf9\u6350\u8d60\u7528\u4e8e\u75ab\u60c5\u9632\u63a7\u7684\u8fdb\u53e3\u7269\u8d44\uff0c\u514d\u5f81\u8fdb\u53e3\u5173\u7a0e\u7b49{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=jiemian.com|access-date=2 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202065401/https://www.jiemian.com/article/3932987.html|archive-date=2 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name=\"auto100\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3933142.html|language=zh-Hans |script-title=zh:\u56fd\u52a1\u9662\u5173\u7a0e\u7a0e\u5219\u59d4\u5458\u4f1a\uff1a\u80ba\u708e\u75ab\u60c5\u8fdb\u53e3\u7269\u8d44\u4e0d\u5b9e\u65bd\u5bf9\u7f8e\u52a0\u5f81\u5173\u7a0e\u63aa\u65bd{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=jiemian.com|access-date=2 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202065401/https://www.jiemian.com/article/3933142.html|archive-date=2 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nThe Ministry of Ecology and Environment issued a notice late in the evening to deploy medical wastewater and urban sewage supervision, regulate emergency medical wastewater treatment, sterilisation and disinfection requirements, in order to prevent the spread of new coronavirus through faeces and sewage,<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3933853.html |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:\u73af\u5883\u90e8\uff1a\u9632\u6b62\u65b0\u578b\u51a0\u72b6\u75c5\u6bd2\u901a\u8fc7\u7caa\u4fbf\u548c\u6c61\u6c34\u6269\u6563\u4f20\u64ad{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=jiemian.com|access-date=2 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202061200/https://www.jiemian.com/article/3933853.html|archive-date=2 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> after the faeces of a patient was tested positive for the virus in [[Shenzhen]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3933661.html|language=zh |script-title=zh:\u6df1\u5733\u5e02\u536b\u5065\u59d4\uff1a\u786e\u8bca\u60a3\u8005\u7caa\u4fbf\u4e2d\u68c0\u6d4b\u51fa\u65b0\u578b\u51a0\u72b6\u75c5\u6bd2RNA\u9633\u6027{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=jiemian.com|access-date=2 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202065358/https://www.jiemian.com/article/3933661.html|archive-date=2 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nThe Department of Civil Affairs of Hubei Province suspends all marriage registrations starting on 3 February 2020.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3932693.html |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:2\u67083\u65e5\u8d77\uff0c\u6e56\u5317\u7701\u5404\u5a5a\u59fb\u767b\u8bb0\u673a\u5173\u6682\u505c\u529e\u7406\u6240\u6709\u5a5a\u59fb\u767b\u8bb0\u4e1a\u52a1{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=jiemian.com|access-date=2 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202065359/https://www.jiemian.com/article/3932693.html|archive-date=2 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n[[Huanggang|Huanggang, Hubei]] implements a much stricter control, allowing only one person from each household every two days to be on the street for purchases, unless for medically-related reasons, required for epidemic control, or as shop workers.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.cnhubei.com/huanggang/p/12673257.html|language=zh-Hans |script-title=zh:\u9ec4\u5188\u53d1\u5e03\u53f2\u4e0a\u6700\u4e25\u51fa\u884c\u7ba1\u63a7\u901a\u77e5\uff0c\u6bcf\u6237\u4e24\u5929\u53ef\u6307\u6d3e1\u4eba\u4e0a\u8857\u91c7\u8d2d|last=|first=|date=|website=news.cnhubei.com|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202143057/http://news.cnhubei.com/huanggang/p/12673257.html|archive-date=2 February 2020|access-date=2 February 2020