ng]] announces implementing the same measure as Huanggang, where every household may send one person every two days outside for purchases, from 00:00 on 2 February to 24:00 on 8 February.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.yicai.com/news/100485610.html |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:\u6e29\u5dde\u5b9e\u884c\u6751(\u5c45)\u6c11\u51fa\u884c\u7ba1\u63a7\uff0c\u6bcf\u6237\u6bcf\u4e24\u5929\u53ef\u6307\u6d3e1\u4eba\u51fa\u95e8\u91c7\u8d2d|last=|first=|date=2 February 2020|website=yicai.com|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202142810/https://www.yicai.com/news/100485610.html|archive-date=2 February 2020|access-date=2 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n[[Huoshenshan Hospital]] completed construction in the morning and was transferred to the military, half a day earlier than scheduled.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3934433.html |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:\u706b\u795e\u5c71\u533b\u9662\u5b8c\u5de5\uff0c\u660e\u65e5\u63a5\u8bca{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=jiemian.com|access-date=2 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202061233/https://www.jiemian.com/article/3934433.html|archive-date=2 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.eeo.com.cn/2020/0202/375401.shtml|language=zh-Hans |script-title=zh:\u6b66\u6c49\u706b\u795e\u5c71\u533b\u9662\u63d0\u524d\u534a\u5929\u79fb\u4ea4 \u96f7\u795e\u5c71\u533b\u96622\u67085\u65e5\u4ea4\u4ed8 - \u7ecf\u6d4e\u89c2\u5bdf\u7f51 \uff0d \u4e13\u4e1a\u8d22\u7ecf\u65b0\u95fb\u7f51\u7ad9|website=eeo.com.cn|access-date=2 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200203154959/http://www.eeo.com.cn/2020/0202/375401.shtml|archive-date=3 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nHubei allows imported and re-imported masks that are unlisted in China to be sold in the provincial market.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3934550.html|language=zh |script-title=zh:\u6e56\u5317\u5141\u8bb8\u672a\u5728\u5883\u5185\