2020|work=The Guardian|access-date=15 February 2020|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077}}</ref> [[People's Bank of China|PBC]] branches reporting to its Guangzhou branch would destroy all cash retrieved from hospitals, agricultural markets, and public transit.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3987904.html |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:\u4eba\u884c\u5e7f\u5dde\u5206\u884c\uff1a\u75ab\u60c5\u671f\u95f4\u533b\u9662\u3001\u519c\u8d38\u5e02\u573a\u548c\u516c\u4ea4\u56de\u6536\u73b0\u949e\u76f4\u63a5\u9500\u6bc1{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=www.jiemian.com|access-date=15 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n=== 16 February ===\nHubei implements \"hard quarantine\" in units of natural villages; no outsiders are to be allowed in and each household is allowed one person every three days to go out for provisions and urgent agricultural material, on designated routes and in limited time.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3992008.html|language=zh |script-title=zh:\u6e56\u5317\u4ee5\u81ea\u7136\u6751\u7ec4\u4e3a\u5355\u5143\u5b9e\u65bd\u786c\u9694\u79bb\uff1a\u6bcf\u6237\u6bcf3\u5929\u53ef\u6d3e\u4e00\u4eba\u91c7\u8d2d{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=www.jiemian.com|access-date=16 February 2020}}</ref> All nonessential public spaces in Hubei are to be closed and all gatherings forbidden.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_6020319|language=zh |script-title=zh:\u6e56\u5317\u5f3a\u5316\u9632\u63a7\uff1a\u6240\u6709\u975e\u5fc5\u9700\u7684\u516c\u5171\u573a\u6240\u4e00\u5f8b\u5173\u95ed\uff0c\u4e00\u5207\u7fa4\u4f17\u805a\u96c6\u6027\u6d3b\u52a8\u4e00\u5f8b\u505c\u6b62\uff01_\u5a92\u4f53_\u6f8e\u6e43\u65b0\u95fb-The Paper|website=www.thepaper.cn|access-date=16 February 2020}}</ref> Following its decision on the previous day, the city of [[Wuxue]] in Huanggang now bans residents and vehicles without medical or epidemic control reasons from the streets. Anyone in violation is to be sent to a stadium for \"centralised compulsory study\" about the laws and epidemic response,<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pearvideo.com/video_1652784 |language=zh-Hans |script-title=zh:\u6b66\u7a74\u4e71\u4e0a\u8857\u7684\u8003\u9ec4\u5188\u5bc6\u5377\uff1f\u5b98\u65b9\u56de\u5e94_\u4e00\u7ebfvideo-\u68a8\u89c6\u9891\u5b98\u7f51-Pear Video|website=www.pearvideo.com|access-date=17 February 2020}}</ref> and any such cars would be seized.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3989346.html|language=zh |script-title=zh:\u6e56\u5317\u9ec4\u5188\u6b66\u7a74\u5e02\u57df\u8303\u56f4\u5185\u5168\u9762\u7981\u51fa\u9650\u884c{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=www.jiemian.com|access-date=15 February 2020}}</ref> All communities in [[Dongcheng District, Beijing]] are required to implement closed management.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3991630.html|language=zh |script-title=zh:\u5317\u4eac\u4e1c\u57ce\u63a8\u52a8\u5168\u90e8784\u4e2a\u5c0f\u533a\u5b9e\u73b0\u5c01\u95ed\u5f0f\u7ba1\u7406{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=www.jiemian.com|access-date=16 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n[[Guizhou]] resumes normal traffic, removing all temporary quarantine checkpoints.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20200217/34248696.html |language=zh-tw |script-title=zh:\u8cb4\u5dde\u64a4\u9664\u57ce\u9109\u4ea4\u901a\u6aa2\u75ab\u9ede1976\u500b\uff0c\u5168\u9762\u6062\u5fa9\u7701\u5167\u4ea4\u901a|date=17 February 2020 |work=Sina News Taiwan|access-date=17 February 2020}}</ref>\n\nThe first two autopsies of patients killed by SARS-CoV-2 were carried out in [[Jinyintan Hospital]]; its pathology was obtained and submitted for testing.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.chinanews.com/gn/2020/02-16/9093707.shtml |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:\u5168\u56fd\u7b2c\u4e00\u4f8b\u3001\u7b2c\u4e8c\u4f8b\u7531\u9057\u4f53\u89e3\u5256\u83b7\u5f97\u7684\u65b0\u51a0\u80ba\u708e\u75c5\u7406\u4eca\u65e5\u88ab\u9001\u68c0-\u4e2d\u65b0\u7f51|website=www.chinanews.com|access-date=16 February 2020}}</ref> A vaccine of the virus developed by national institutions began its animal experiment stage; clinical trials are expected in April at the earliest.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3990167.html|language=zh-Hans |script-title=zh:\u4e2d\u56fd\u5f00\u53d1\u65b0\u51a0\u75ab\u82d7\u5f00\u59cb\u52a8\u7269\u8bd5\u9a8c\uff0c\u6700\u5feb4\u6708\u8fdb\u5165\u4e34\u5e8a{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=www.jiemian.com|access-date=16 February 2020}}</ref>\n\nThe NHC urges for the reduction of the workload of grassroots workers, asking for all legally unnecessary procedures to be halted.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3991486.html |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:\u536b\u5065\u59d4\u660e\u786e\u8981\u51cf\u8f7b\u57fa\u5c42\u9632\u75ab\u4eba\u5458\u8d1f\u62c5\uff1a\u8ba9\u57fa\u5c42\u4eba\u5458\u7cbe\u529b\u653e\u5728\u4e00\u7ebf{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=www.jiemian.com|access-date=16 February 2020}}</ref> The [[General Administration of Customs]] has introduced 10 measures to support foreign trade enterprises to resume production.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3990570.html |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:\u6d77\u5173\u603b\u7f72\uff1a10\u6761\u63aa\u65bd\u652f\u6301\u5916\u8d38\u4f01\u4e1a\u6293\u7d27\u590d\u5de5\u751f\u4ea7\uff0c\u4fc3\u8fdb\u5916\u8d38\u7a33\u589e\u957f{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=www.jiemian.com|access-date=16 February 2020}}</ref> Instructed by the Office of the [[State Council of the People's Republic of China|State Council]], [[Alipay]] is now developing a national unified system of \"Health Code\" first used in [[Hangzhou]] on 11 Feb, a digital health evaluation certificate for the safe resumption of business.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3990430.html |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:\u676d\u5dde\u5065\u5eb7\u7801\u