rus.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-health-mobileworld-amazon-com-idUSKBN2030QV|title=Amazon pulls out of major Barcelona telecoms conference over coronavirus|date=9 February 2020|work=Reuters|access-date=9 February 2020|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/business-51438845|title=Coronavirus: Amazon pulls out of major tech show|date=9 February 2020|work=BBC News|access-date=9 February 2020|language=en-GB}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/02/10/tech/mobile-world-congress-coronavirus/index.html|title=Amazon, Sony and Ericsson pull out of Mobile World Congress over coronavirus fears|last=Business|first=Hanna Ziady, CNN|website=CNN|access-date=10 February 2020}}</ref>\n\nThe virus daily death toll reaches a new record of 97 people dead from the virus in a single day.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/10/world/asia/coronavirus-china.html|title=Coronavirus Updates: 97 Dead in Single Day, a New Daily Record|date=10 February 2020|work=The New York Times|access-date=10 February 2020|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-51439450|title=Coronavirus kills 97 in deadliest day so far|date=10 February 2020|work=BBC News|access-date=10 February 2020|language=en-GB}}</ref>\n\nAsian stock markets fell and went into red due to investor fears relating to the virus impact on the economy.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.msn.com/en-us/finance/markets/asian-markets-fall-on-coronavirus-impact-woes/ar-BBZPlxo|title=Asian markets fall on coronavirus impact woes|website=www.msn.com|access-date=10 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://finance.yahoo.com/news/asian-markets-fall-coronavirus-concerns-012122260.html|title=Asian markets stem losses as China returns to work but sentiment jittery|website=finance.yahoo.com|language=en-US|access-date=10 February 2020}}</ref>\n\nThe plane that was taking people who lived in Brazil or were ci