avirus: Passengers disembark from Diamond Princess in Japan |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-51555420 |website=BBC |accessdate=19 February 2020 |date=19 February 2020}}</ref> 79 more cases are confirmed on the cruise ship, bringing the total number to 621.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Woods |first1=Amanda |title=Diamond Princess reports 79 more coronavirus cases as expert slams 'completely inadequate' quarantine |url=https://nypost.com/2020/02/19/diamond-princess-reports-79-more-coronavirus-cases-as-expert-slams-ships-completely-inadequate-quarantine/ |website=New York Post |accessdate=19 February 2020 |date=19 February 2020}}</ref> Japan also reported 10 new cases not aboard the cruise ship.\n\n=== 20 February ===\n'''WHO''' Situation Report 31:<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.who.int/docs/default-source/coronaviruse/situation-reports/20200220-sitrep-31-covid-19.pdf?sfvrsn=dfd11d24_2|title=Situation Report 31|last=|first=|date=|website=World Health Organization|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=20 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n* Hong Kong confirmed four more cases, bringing the total number to 69.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Sum |first1=Lok-kei |last2=Leung |first2=Kanis |last3=Cheung |first3=Elizabeth |last4=Leung |first4=Christy \n|last5=Lo |first5=Clifford |title=Coronavirus: officer becomes 69th case in Hong Kong after attending party with 59 others, all of whom have been asked to avoid public |url=https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/health-environment/article/3051553/coronavirus-hong-kong-government-extends-work |website=South China Morning Post |accessdate=21 February 2020 |date=20 February 2020}}</ref>\n* Iran confirmed three more cases, bringing the total number to five.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Haghdoost |first1=Yasna |title=Iran Reports Three Confirmed Coronavirus Cases After Two Deaths |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-02-20/iran-reports-three-confirmed-coronavirus-cases-after-two-deaths |website=Bloomberg |accessdate=20 February 2