ountry's total to 11.<ref>{{cite web |title=Fler fall uppt\u00e4ckta av covid-19 (in Swedish) |url=https://www.folkhalsomyndigheten.se/nyheter-och-press/nyhetsarkiv/2020/februari/fler-fall-upptackta-av-covid-19/ |publisher=Public Health Agency of Sweden |accessdate=28 February 2020 |date=28 February 2020}}</ref>\n* Switzerland's cases increased to 15.<ref>{{cite web |title=New coronavirus |url=https://www.bag.admin.ch/bag/en/home/krankheiten/ausbrueche-epidemien-pandemien/aktuelle-ausbrueche-epidemien/novel-cov.html |website=Federal Office of Public Health (Switzerland) |accessdate=28 February 2020 |date=28 February 2020}}</ref>\n* Taiwan confirmed two additional cases, taking its total to 34.<ref>{{cite web |title=\u65b0\u589e2\u4f8b\u78ba\u8a3a\uff0c\u6307\u63ee\u4e2d\u5fc3\u5bc6\u5207\u8ffd\u8e64\u63a5\u89f8\u8005 |url=https://www.cdc.gov.tw/Bulletin/Detail/HBpziqvnQZesFtrAyQFeJg?typeid=9 |publisher=Taiwan Centers for Disease Control |accessdate=28 February 2020 |date=28 February 2020}}</ref>\n* Thailand confirmed an additional case, taking the overall number to 41.<ref>{{cite web |title=Thailand reports one new coronavirus case, total reaches 41 - health official |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-health-thailand-case-idUSKCN20M0FS |publisher=Reuters |accessdate=28 February 2020 |date=28 February 2020}}</ref>\n* The United Kingdom reported its 17th and 18th cases, in people who had travelled from Iran, and its 19th case and the first in Wales, being someone who had travelled from Northern Italy.<ref>{{cite web |title=Coronavirus: First case confirmed in Wales |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-51673068 |publisher=BBC |accessdate=28 February 2020 |date=28 February 2020}}</ref> In the evening, the 20th case was confirmed, the first case of being passed on in the UK from an unknown source.<ref>{{cite web |title=Coronavirus passed on within UK for first time as 20th case confirmed |url=https://www.thenorthernecho.co.uk/news/national/18270758.coronavirus-passed-within-uk-first-time-20th-case-confirmed/ |publisher=The Northern Echo |accessdate=28 February 2020 |date=28 February 2020}}</ref>\n* The United States confirmed 4 more cases, including 2 former passengers of ''Diamond Princess''.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Woolfolk |first1=John |last2=Krieger |first2=Lisa M. |title=Second U.S. coronavirus case of unknown origin confirmed in Santa Clara County; third reported in Oregon |url=https://www.mercurynews.com/santa-clara-county-announces-new-coronavirus-case |website=The Mercury News |accessdate=28 February 2020 |date=28 February 2020}}</ref> Washington state authorities later confirmed two additional presumptive cases, bringing its total to 66. One had recently returned from South Korea, and the other case was unrelated and locally acquired.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Connelly |first1=Eileen AJ |title=Two new coronavirus cases identified in Washington state |url=https://nypost.com/2020/02/29/two-new-coronavirus-cases-identified-in-washington-state/ |website=New York Post |accessdate=29 February 2020 |date=29 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Connelly |first1=Eileen AJ |title=Two new coronavirus cases identified in Washington state |url=https://nypost.com/2020/02/29/two-new-coronavirus-cases-identified-in-washington-state/ |website=New York Post |accessdate=29 February 2020 |date=28 February 2020}}</ref>\n* SARS-CoV-2 was detected for the first time in tears and conjunctival secretions (pink eye) of a patient. This was only detected in 1 out of the 30 patients that were tested. The excerpt from the study stated, \"In the study of this small sample, we used conjunctival test paper to obtain tears and conjunctival secretions of 30 patients for standard RT-PCR assay. Only one patient with conjunctivitis found viral RNA in his tear fluid and conjunctival secretion twice.\"<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Xia |first1=Jianhua |last2=Tong |first2=Jianping |last3=Liu |first3=Mengyun |last4=Shen |first4=Ye |last5=Guo |first5=Dongyu |title=Evaluation of coronavirus in tears and conjunctival secretions of patients with SARS\u2010CoV\u20102 infection |journal=Journal of Medical Virology |date=26 February 2020 |doi=10.1002/jmv.25725 |pmid=32100876 |doi-access=free }}</ref>\n\n=== 29 February ===\n'''WHO''' Situation Report 40:<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.who.int/docs/default-source/coronaviruse/situation-reports/20200229-sitrep-40-covid-19.pdf?sfvrsn=7203e653_2|title=Situation Report 40|last=|first=|date=|website=World Health Organization|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=29 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n* Australia confirmed one more case, bringing the total number to 25.<ref name=\"Aus29Feb\">{{cite web |title=Coronavirus: Australia to bar foreign nationals arriving from Iran |url=https://www.scmp.com/news/asia/australasia/article/3053003/coronavirus-australia-bar-foreign-nationals-arriving-iran |website=South China Morning Post |accessdate=29 February 2020 |date=29 February 2020}}</ref>\n* Austria confirmed four new cases, bringing the total to 10.<ref>{{cite web |title=Confirmed COVID-19 cases in Austria rise to 10 |url=https://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2020-03/01/c_138831006.htm |publisher=Xinhua |accessdate=29 February 2020}}</ref>\n* Azerbaijan reported two new cases, both recently returned from Iran.<ref>{{cite web |title=\u0423 \u0434\u0432\u0443\u0445 \u0433\u0440\u0430\u0436\u0434\u0430\u043d \u0410\u0437\u0435\u0440\u0431\u0430\u0439\u0434\u0436\u0430\u043d\u0430, \u0432\u0435\u0440\u043d\u0443\u0432\u0448\u0438\u0445\u0441\u044f \u0438\u0437 \u0418\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0430, \u0432\u044b\u044f\u0432\u043b\u0435\u043d\u044b \u0441\u0438\u043c\u043f\u0442\u043e\u043c\u044b \u043a\u043e\u0440\u043e\u043d\u0430\u0432\u0438\u0440\u0443\u0441\u0430 |url=https://www.trend.az/azerbaijan/society/3199863.html |publisher=Trend news agency |accessdate=1 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200229141434/https://www.trend.az/azerbaijan/society/3199863.html |archive