55703/ |website=Iraqi Ministry of Health |accessdate=29 February 2020 |date=29 February 2020}}</ref>\n* Ireland confirmed its first case, associated with travel to northern Italy.<ref>{{cite web |title=Statement from the National Public Health Emergency Team |url=https://bnonews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/ireland.png |website=BNO News |accessdate=29 February 2020 |date=29 February 2020}}</ref>\n* Italy confirmed 239 new cases and 8 new deaths, bringing it to 1,128 cases and 29 deaths.<ref>{{cite web |title=Coronavirus in Italia: gli ultimi aggiornamenti (in Italian) |url=https://www.repubblica.it/cronaca/2020/02/22/news/coronavirus_in_italia_aggiornamento_ora_per_ora-249241616/ |publisher=la Repuubblica |accessdate=29 February 2020|date=22 February 2020 }}</ref> \n* Lebanon confirmed three more cases, bringing the total number of cases to seven.<ref>{{cite news |title=Lebanon confirms three new cases of coronavirus, bringing total to seven: NNA |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-health-lebanon/lebanon-confirms-three-new-cases-of-coronavirus-bringing-total-to-seven-nna-idUSKBN20N0PS |agency=Reuters |accessdate=29 February 2020|date=29 February 2020 }}</ref>\n* Luxembourg confirmed its first case.<ref>{{cite web |title=Breaking news |url=https://twitter.com/joel_mossong/status/1233839581633687553 |website=Joel Mossong |accessdate=29 February 2020 |date=29 February 2020}}</ref>\n* Mexico confirmed two more cases, one man in the State of Mexico who participated in the same trip to Bergamo, Italy, that the first two infected made,<ref>{{cite web |title=Los tres portadores de coronavirus en M\u00e9xico arribaron de Italia (in Spanish) |url=https://politica.expansion.mx/mexico/2020/02/28/los-tres-portadores-de-coronavirus-en-mexico-arribaron-de-italia |publisher=Expansi\u00f3n |accessdate= 29 February 2020|date=29 February 2020 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Ya lleg\u00f3 el coronavirus; M\u00e9xico confirma tres casos; hay otros tres sospechosos (in Spanish) |url=https://www.excelsior.com.mx/nacional/ya-llego-el-coronavirus-mexico-confirma-tres-casos-hay-otros-tres-sospechosos/1367009 |publisher=Excelsior |accessdate= 29 February 2020|date=29 February 2020 }}</ref> and a woman in Coahuila who traveled to Milan, Italy, between January and February,<ref>{{cite web |title=Hay un caso confirmado de coronavirus en Torre\u00f3n, dice gobernador (in Spanish) |url=https://www.milenio.com/estados/coronavirus-torreon-confirma-miguel-riquelme-caso-covid19 |publisher=Milenio |accessdate= 29 February 2020}}</ref> bringing the total to 4.\n* The Netherlands confirmed four additional cases, bringing the total to 6.<ref>{{cite web |title=Gezinsleden corona-pati\u00ebnten Amsterdam en Tilburg ook besmet (in Dutch) |url=https://nos.nl/artikel/2325115-gezinsleden-corona-patienten-amsterdam-en-tilburg-ook-besmet.html |website=nos.nl}}</ref> A seventh case was later confirmed.<ref>{{cite web |title=Pati\u00ebnt met COVID-19 in Delft (in Dutch) |url=https://www.rivm.nl/nieuws/patient-met-covid-19-in-delft |publisher=National Institute for Public Health |accessdate=1 March 2020}}</ref>\n* Norway confirmed nine new cases, bringing the total to 15.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Nikel |first1=David |title=Coronavirus in Norway: The Latest News on the COVID-19 Outbreak |url=https://www.lifeinnorway.net/coronavirus-in-norway/ |website=Life in Norway |accessdate=29 February 2020 |date=29 February 2020}}</ref>\n* Pakistan confirmed two mores cases, bringing its total to 4. One is a person from Karachi who had recently traveled to Iran, and the other case was in the Federal Area.<ref>{{cite web |title=Coronavirus outbreak |url=https://www.dawn.com/live-blog/ |website=Twitter |publisher=Dawn |accessdate=29 February 2020 |date=29 February 2020}}</ref>\n* Qatar confirmed its first case, a Qatari national who had recently returned from Iran.<ref>{{cite web |title=The Ministry of Public Health announces the registration of the first confirmed case of coronaviru