sued a notice late in the evening to deploy medical wastewater and urban sewage supervision, regulate emergency medical wastewater treatment, sterilisation and disinfection requirements, in order to prevent the spread of new coronavirus through faeces and sewage,<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3933853.html |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:\u73af\u5883\u90e8\uff1a\u9632\u6b62\u65b0\u578b\u51a0\u72b6\u75c5\u6bd2\u901a\u8fc7\u7caa\u4fbf\u548c\u6c61\u6c34\u6269\u6563\u4f20\u64ad{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=jiemian.com|access-date=2 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202061200/https://www.jiemian.com/article/3933853.html|archive-date=2 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> after the faeces of a patient was tested positive for the virus in [[Shenzhen]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3933661.html|language=zh |script-title=zh:\u6df1\u5733\u5e02\u536b\u5065\u59d4\uff1a\u786e\u8bca\u60a3\u8005\u7caa\u4fbf\u4e2d\u68c0\u6d4b\u51fa\u65b0\u578b\u51a0\u72b6\u75c5\u6bd2RNA\u9633\u6027{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=jiemian.com|access-date=2 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202065358/https://www.jiemian.com/article/3933661.html|archive-date=2 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nThe Department of Civil Affairs of Hubei Province suspends all marriage registrations starting on 3 February 2020.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3932693.html |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:2\u67083\u65e5\u8d77\uff0c\u6e56\u5317\u7701\u5404\u5a5a\u59fb\u767b\u8bb0\u673a\u5173\u6682\u505c\u529e\u7406\u6240\u6709\u5a5a\u59fb\u767b\u8bb0\u4e1a\u52a1{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=jiemian.com|access-date=2 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202065359/https://www.jiemian.com/article/3932693.html|archive-date=2 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n[[Huanggang|Huanggang, Hubei]] implements a much stricter control, allowing only one person from each household every two days to be on the street for purchases, unless for medically-related reasons, required for epidemic control, or as shop workers.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.cnhubei.com/huanggang/p/12673257.html|language=zh-Hans |script-title=zh:\u9ec4\u5188\u53d1\u5e03\u53f2\u4e0a\u6700\u4e25\u51fa\u884c\u7ba1\u63a7\u901a\u77e5\uff0c\u6bcf\u6237\u4e24\u5929\u53ef\u6307\u6d3e1\u4eba\u4e0a\u8857\u91c7\u8d2d|last=|first=|date=|website=news.cnhubei.com|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202143057/http://news.cnhubei.com/huanggang/p/12673257.html|archive-date=2 February 2020|access-date=2 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n[[Alibaba Group]] announced free taxi service for health professionals in Wuhan.<ref name=\"auto100\" />\n\nHunan government required companies in the province not to resume business before 24:00 on 9 February; the new semester is not to start earlier than 17 February for primary and secondary schools and kindergartens, and 24 February for post-secondary institutions.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3931335.html|language=zh |script-title=zh:\u6e56\u5357\u5ef6\u8fdf\u4f01\u4e1a\u590d\u5de5\u65f6\u95f4\u4e0d\u65e9\u4e8e2\u67089\u65e524\u65f6{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=jiemian.com|access-date=2 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202065356/https://www.jiemian.com/article/3931335.html|archive-date=2 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> Tianjin government issued a notice to postpone business resumption and the start of the new semester.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.chinanews.com/gn/2020/02-01/9074793.shtml |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:\u5929\u6d25\u5ef6\u8fdf\u4f01\u4e1a\u590d\u5de5\u548c\u5b66\u6821\u5f00\u5b66-\u4e2d\u65b0\u7f51|website=chinanews.com|access-date=2 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202141545/http://www.chinanews.com/gn/2020/02-01/9074793.shtml|archive-date=2 F