use the filming of all films and TV dramas in mainland China during the epidemic.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3932933.html|language=zh-Hans |script-title=zh:\u4e2d\u56fd\u5e7f\u64ad\u7535\u89c6\u793e\u4f1a\u7ec4\u7ec7\u8054\u5408\u4f1a\u7535\u89c6\u5236\u7247\u59d4\u5458\u4f1a\uff1a\u75ab\u60c5\u671f\u95f4\u505c\u6b62\u5f71\u89c6\u5267\u62cd\u6444{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=jiemian.com|access-date=2 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202065400/https://www.jiemian.com/article/3932933.html|archive-date=2 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n310 Hubei citizens were repatriated from Thailand, Malaysia, and Japan.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3931691.html|language=zh-Hans |script-title=zh:\u4e2d\u56fd\u653f\u5e9c\u5305\u673a\u63a5\u56de\u6ede\u7559\u56fd\u5916\u7684\u6e56\u5317\u540c\u80de310\u4eba{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=jiemian.com|access-date=2 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202065357/https://www.jiemian.com/article/3931691.html|archive-date=2 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n[[Apple Inc.]] temporarily closed all Apple Stores in mainland China until 24:00 on 9 February.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3932498.html |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:\u82f9\u679c\u5ba3\u5e03\u4e34\u65f6\u5173\u95ed\u4e2d\u56fd\u5927\u9646Apple Store\u96f6\u552e\u5e97{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=jiemian.com|access-date=2 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202065357/https://www.jiemian.com/article/3932498.html|archive-date=2 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nChina's [[National Health Commission]] (NHC) announced new regulations Saturday requiring that all who lose their lives to the coronavirus must be cremated at the nearest facility. \"No farewell ceremonies or other funeral activities involving the corpse shall be held,\" according to the new ruling.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/china-bans-funerals-for-coronavirus-victims-as-death-toll-rises-2020-2|title=China says Wuhan coronavirus victims who die should be quickly cremated without funerals as death toll rises|last=Pickrell|first=Ryan|website=Business Insider|access-date=8 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200204043336/https://www.businessinsider.com/china-bans-funerals-for-coronavirus-victims-as-death-toll-rises-2020-2|archive-date=4 February 2020|url-status=live|date=2 February 2020}}</ref>\n\nThe [[Badminton World Federation]] announced it has postponed the [[2020 Lingshui China Masters]] tournament, originally scheduled to be held from 25 February to 1 March.<ref>{{cite news |title=BWF Statement on Postponement of Lingshui China Masters |url=https://bwfbadminton.com/news-single/2020/02/01/bwf-statement-on-postponement-of-lingshui-china-masters/ |publisher=Badminton World Federation |accessdate=2 February 2020 |date=1 February 2020 |work=bwfbadminton.com}}</ref>\n\n=== 2 February ===\nWuhan's Epidemic Prevention and Control Headquarters<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_5738051 |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:\u4e5d\u5dde\u901a\uff1a\u6628\u8d77\u534f\u52a9\u6b66\u6c49\u5e02\u7ea2\u5341\u5b57\u4f1a\u8fdb\u884c\u4ed3\u50a8\u8fd0\u8425\u7ba1\u7406\uff0c\u63d0\u9ad8\u6548\u7387|website=thepaper.cn|access-date=2 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202083827/https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_5738051|archive-date=2 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> arranged for [[Jointown Pharmaceutical]] to overtake the warehouse management of [[Hubei Red Cross|Wuhan Red Cross]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.iyiou.com/p/122862.html |language=zh-Hans |script-title=zh:\u534f\u52a9\u6b66\u6c49\u7ea2\u4f1a\u7ba1\u7406\u7269\u8d44\uff0c\u4e5d\u5dde\u901a\u8981\u8fd9\u4e48\u505a|website=iyiou.com|access-date=2 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/2020