-51485559 |website=BBC News |date=14 February 2020 |language=zh-Hans |trans-title=Treating the novel coronavirus: the empirical Western medicine and the self-positioning Chinese medicine}}</ref> The same official file that contains the prescription also demands that all patients in Wuhan be treated by TCM.<ref>{{cite web |language=zh-Hans |script-title=zh:\u6b66\u6c49\u8981\u6c42\u6240\u6709\u60a3\u8005\u5fc5\u987b\u5403\u4e2d\u836f \u7f51\u6c11\u8d28\u7591 |url=https://www.epochtimes.com/gb/20/2/4/n11842894.htm |website=Epoch Times |accessdate=15 February 2020 |date=4 February 2020 |trans-title=Wuhan wants all patients put on TCM; Netizens question}}</ref>\n\n[[Wenzhou|Wenzhou, Zhejiang]] announces implementing the same measure as Huanggang, where every household may send one person every two days outside for purchases, from 00:00 on 2 February to 24:00 on 8 February.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.yicai.com/news/100485610.html |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:\u6e29\u5dde\u5b9e\u884c\u6751(\u5c45)\u6c11\u51fa\u884c\u7ba1\u63a7\uff0c\u6bcf\u6237\u6bcf\u4e24\u5929\u53ef\u6307\u6d3e1\u4eba\u51fa\u95e8\u91c7\u8d2d|last=|first=|date=2 February 2020|website=yicai.com|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202142810/https://www.yicai.com/news/100485610.html|archive-date=2 February 2020|access-date=2 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n[[Huoshenshan Hospital]] completed construction in the morning and was transferred to the military, half a day earlier than scheduled.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3934433.html |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:\u706b\u795e\u5c71\u533b\u9662\u5b8c\u5de5\uff0c\u660e\u65e5\u63a5\u8bca{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=jiemian.com|access-date=2 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202061233/https://www.jiemian.com/article/3934433.html|archive-date=2 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.eeo.com.cn/2020/0202/375401.shtml|language=zh-Hans |