-leak-by-tencent-revealing-over-24000-deaths-in-china-due-to-coronavirus-fact-check|title=Doctored Screenshots Claim China's Coronavirus Deaths Over 24,000|date=7 February 2020|website=The Quint|language=en|access-date=8 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.open.online/2020/02/07/diffusione-coronavirus-tencent-ha-pubblicato-i-veri-dati-nascosti-dal-governo-cinese-lanalisi/|title=Diffusione Coronavirus: Tencent ha pubblicato i veri dati nascosti dal governo cinese? L'analisi|date=7 February 2020|website=Open|language=it-IT|access-date=8 February 2020}}</ref>\n\nChina announces that they will halve the tariff on US$75 billion goods imported from America, and Chinese official media [[Global Times]] commented that China is considering the use of disaster provision in the US-China Phase One trade deal, which was signed in the previous month.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=379605|title=\u3010\u95dc\u7a05\u6e1b\u534a\u3011\u74b0\u6642\uff1a\u4e2d\u570b\u6216\u6b63\u8003\u616e\u4f7f\u7528\u8cbf\u5354\u4e2d\u7684\u707d\u96e3\u689d\u6b3e|date=6 February 2020|work=Now News}}</ref>\n\n=== 7 February ===\n[[Li Wenliang (doctor)|Li Wenliang]] dies.  Wenliang was a 34-year-old ophthalmologist at Wuhan Central Hospital and one of eight doctors who tried to share information about the coronavirus when it was first emerging, only to be reprimanded by Wuhan police.  He likely became infected by the coronavirus while treating patients during January.  His death from complications of the infection is declared at 2:58&nbsp;a.m. local time.<ref name=\"auto23\" /><ref name=\"peopleswar\">{{cite news|last1=Lee|first1=Se Young|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-health/china-wages-peoples-war-on-coronavirus-as-cruises-companies-hit-idUSKBN20003J|title=Cruise line bans China citizens; Outrage as doctor who sounded coronavirus alarm dies|date=7 February 2020|accessdate=8 February 2020|agency=Reuters|last2=Goh|first2=Brenda|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200206210718/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-health/china-wages-peoples-war-on-coronavirus-as-cruises-companies-hit-idUSKBN20003J|archive-date=6 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nOn 7 February, the Joint Defence and Control Mechanism of the State Council introduced a scheme of \"one province for one city\", where 16 provinces would provide medical force support for every city in Hubei except Wuhan.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bjnews.com.cn/news/2020/02/07/685879.html|language=zh-Hans |script-title=zh:\u56fd\u5bb6\u536b\u5065\u59d4\uff1a16\u7701\u4efd\u201c\u4e00\u7701\u5305\u4e00\u5e02\u201d\u652f\u63f4\u6e56\u5317|last=www.bjnews.com.cn|website=www.bjnews.com.cn|access-date=10 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_5857397 |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:16\u7701\u4efd\u4e00\u7701\u5305\u4e00\u5e02\u652f\u63f4\u6e56\u5317\u540d\u5355\u516c\u5e03\uff1a\u6e56\u5317\u5468\u8fb9\u7701\u4efd\u5747\u9886\u547d_\u6297\u75ab_\u6f8e\u6e43\u65b0\u95fb-The Paper|website=www.thepaper.cn|access-date=10 February 2020}}</ref>\n\nHangzhou imposed a temporary ban on retail pharmacies selling fever and cough medicines, asking citizens with the symptoms to see a doctor instead.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3958003.html |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:\u676d\u5dde\u6682\u505c\u6240\u6709\u96f6\u552e\u836f\u5e97\u9500\u552e\u53d1\u70e7\u54b3\u55fd\u836f\u54c1{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=www.jiemian.com|access-date=9 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n=== 8 February ===\n\nShenzhen<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3958355.html|language=zh |script-title=zh:\u6df1\u5733\uff1a\u514d\u9664\u5168\u5e02\u5de5\u5546\u4f01\u4e1a2\u6708\u4efd\u5f53\u6708\u7f34\u4ea4\u4e24\u90e8\u5236\u7535\u8d39\u4e2d\u7684\u57fa\u672c\u7535\u8d39{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=www.jiemian.com|access-date=8 February 2020}}</ref><ref