n.com/article/3981924.html |language=zh-cn |script-title=zh:\u5e7f\u897f\u518d\u6b21\u8c03\u6574\u5ef6\u8fdf\u5f00\u5b66\u65f6\u95f4\uff0c\u5404\u7ea7\u5404\u7c7b\u5b66\u68213\u67081\u65e5\u524d\u4e0d\u5f97\u5f00\u5b66{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=www.jiemian.com|access-date=14 February 2020}}</ref>\n\nWuhan enacts a new rule prohibiting people from leaving their neighbourhoods for non-medical reasons, updating the curfew to a full lockdown.<ref>{{cite news |title=Wuhan Sharply Tightens Quarantines on Residents: Virus Update |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-02-13/u-s-ramps-up-criticism-hubei-data-awaited-virus-update |accessdate=15 February 2020 |agency=Bloomberg}}</ref>\n\n=== 14 February ===\nThe central districts of [[Yunmeng County]] in [[Xiaogan|Xiaogan, Hubei]] entered [[wartime control]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3984076.html|language=zh |script-title=zh:\u6e56\u5317\u4e91\u68a6\u53bf\u57ce\u533a\u5b9e\u65bd\u6218\u65f6\u7ba1\u5236{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=www.jiemian.com|access-date=14 February 2020}}</ref> [[Huanggang|Huanggang, Hubei]] escalated control starting 00:00, prohibiting non-essential persons or vehicles from entering and exiting communities and initiating the organised distribution of basic necessities.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nbd.com.cn/articles/2020-02-13/1408101.html|language=zh |script-title=zh:\u6e56\u5317\u53c8\u4e00\u533a\u53bf\u5c06\u5b9e\u65bd\u201c\u6218\u65f6\u7ba1\u7406\u201d\uff01\u9ec4\u5188\u7ba1\u63a7\u5347\u7ea7\uff1a\u5c0f\u533a\u5168\u5c01\u95ed\uff0c\u751f\u6d3b\u5fc5\u9700\u54c1\u7edf\u4e00\u914d\u9001\uff01\u4eca\u665a\uff0c\u4e2d\u592e\u53c8\u53d1\u8bdd\u4e86 {{!}} \u6bcf\u7ecf\u7f51|website=www.nbd.com.cn|access-date=14 February 2020}}</ref>\n\nA new test kit was developed by a team led by [[Zhong Nanshan]], able to yield a result in fifteen minutes with a very high sensitivity and expected to raise the positive detection rate.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3986703.html|language=zh-Hans |script-title=zh:\u949f\u5357\u5c71\u6307\u5bfc\u7814\u5236\u51fa\u5feb\u901f\u68c0\u6d4b\u8bd5\u5242\u76d2\uff0c\u63d0\u9ad8\u9633\u6027\u68c0\u51fa\u7387{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=www.jiemian.com|access-date=15 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3987102.html|language=zh-Hans |script-title=zh:\u949f\u5357\u5c71\u9662\u58eb\u6307\u5bfc\u7814\u53d1\u5feb\u901f\u68c0\u6d4b\u8bd5\u5242\u76d2\uff0c\u91c7\u4e00\u6ef4\u884015\u5206\u949f\u5185\u53ef\u51fa\u7ed3\u679c{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=www.jiemian.com|access-date=15 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n[[Huanggang]] decided to convert another hospital as a secondary medical institution for COVID-19, after [[Dabie Mountain Regional Medical Centre]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3986588.html|language=zh |script-title=zh:\u6e56\u5317\u9ec4\u5188\u518d\u9020\u4e00\u6240\u5e94\u6025\u540e\u5907\u533b\u9662{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=www.jiemian.com|access-date=15 February 2020}}</ref> [[Xiantao|Xiantao, Hubei]] implemented mask ex-factory price control, requiring the ex-factory price of single use medical masks not to exceed \u00a51.20 (US$0.172) each and non-medical ones \u00a51.00 (US$0.143) each.\n\nBeijing required all persons returning to the city to self-quarantine for 14 days.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3986548.html|language=zh |script-title=zh:\u5317\u4eac\uff1a\u5373\u65e5\u8d77\u6240\u6709\u8fd4\u4eac\u4eba\u5458\u5e94\u5c45\u5bb6\u6216\u96c6\u4e2d\u89c2\u5bdf14\u5929|last=|first=|date=14 February 2020|website=jiemian.com|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=15 February 2020}}</ref>\n\nShenzhen Metro would start using [[real-name system]] starting 16 Feb for epidemic tracing, with passengers able to self-register the carriages they ride i