ong-jewelry-trade-fairs-are-rescheduled-due-to-coronavirus/|title=Two Hong Kong Jewelry Trade Fairs Are Rescheduled Due To Coronavirus|last=DeMarco|first=Anthony|website=Forbes|language=en|access-date=7 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200207002750/https://www.forbes.com/sites/anthonydemarco/2020/02/06/two-hong-kong-jewelry-trade-fairs-are-rescheduled-due-to-coronavirus/|archive-date=7 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>  [[Art Basel Hong Kong]] international art fair, that was being held in March also gets cancelled due to the virus epidemic.<ref name=\":13\" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Health/wireStory/latest-hong-kong-cancels-major-art-fair-amid-68814096|title=The Latest: Japan's 4th evacuation flight lands from Wuhan|website=ABC News|language=en|access-date=7 February 2020}}</ref>\n\nThe Canadian evacuation plane landed in [[British Columbia]] for refueling. The plane was also carrying Chinese nationals and citizens who have valid visas for Canada, these were for escorting Canadian minors. The planes final destination is [[CFB Trenton]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.msn.com/en-ca/news/canada/plane-carrying-176-canadians-from-wuhan-china-lands-in-british-columbia/ar-BBZJK1a|title=Plane carrying 176 Canadians from Wuhan, China lands in British Columbia|website=www.msn.com|access-date=7 February 2020}}</ref>\n\nContinuing the evacuation of American citizens from Wuhan, a rescue plane is landing in [[Omaha, Nebraska]] today.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.knopnews2.com/video/?vid=567656052|title=Coronavirus Rescue Plane Lands in Omaha|website=www.knopnews2.com}}</ref>  Others are landing near San Diego, California and San Antonio, Texas today; two passengers are stated as having symptoms of the virus.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://foxsanantonio.com/news/local/two-americans-on-evacuation-planes-showing-symptoms-of-coronavirus-fox-news-reports|title=WATCH NEW INFO: Coronavirus evacuees now quarantined in San Antonio|last=Galli|