ases Double On Quarantined Cruise Ship. Is It Time To Evacuate Passengers?|last=Forster|first=Victoria|website=Forbes|language=en|access-date=11 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/10/world/asia/coronavirus-china.html|title=Coronavirus Updates: A Grim Landmark as Official Death Toll in China Tops 1,000|date=11 February 2020|work=The New York Times|access-date=11 February 2020|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331}}</ref>\n\nThe virus is lowering crude prices worldwide, as China's demand for crude oil decreases due to shutdowns, lockdowns, fears, and other measures.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/02/11/coronavirus-live-updates-china-hubei.html|title=Coronavirus live updates: China death toll tops 1,000|last=Choudhury|first=Saheli Roy|date=10 February 2020|website=CNBC|language=en|access-date=11 February 2020}}</ref>  [[Price of oil|Oil prices]] has just reached a 1-year low again, and has been falling for 5 weeks.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.marketwatch.com/story/oil-edges-lower-as-coronavirus-takes-toll-on-china-crude-demand-2020-02-10|title=Oil drops back to 1-year low as coronavirus takes toll on China crude demand|last=Watts|first=Myra P. Saefong, William|website=MarketWatch|language=en-US|access-date=11 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Toy|first=Sarah|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/oil-prices-swing-as-investors-weigh-coronavirus-fallout-11581094414|title=Oil Falls for Fifth Week as Investors Weigh Coronavirus Fallout|date=7 February 2020|work=Wall Street Journal|access-date=11 February 2020|language=en-US|issn=0099-9660}}</ref>\n\n[[South Korea]] has advised travellers to delay travel to countries and territories hit by the coronavirus; mentioned are Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand, Vietnam, Japan, and Taiwan in addition to mainland China.<ref name=\"TA11Feb\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/wuhan-coronavirus-travel-advisories-to-singapore-12422306 |title=Coronavirus: South K