095/noticia/Noticia/Real_Madrid_turns_106_(I).htm Real Madrid turns 106 (I)] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081229094130/http://www.realmadrid.com/cs/Satellite/en/1202730681095/noticia/Noticia/Real_Madrid_turns_106_%28I%29.htm |date=29 December 2008 }}</ref>\n\n==Competitions==\n\n===Madrid Championship===\n{{Footballbox collapsible\n|date=12 March 1911\n|time=\n|round = Round 1\n|team1=Madrid FC\n|score=3\u20131\n|report=\n|team2=[[Real Sociedad Gimn\u00e1stica Espa\u00f1ola|RS Gimn\u00e1stica]]\n|goals1=[[Francisco P\u00e9rez de Guzm\u00e1n|Guzm\u00e1n]] {{goal}}<br />[[Luis Saura del Pan|Saura]] {{goal}}{{goal}}\n|goals2={{goal}} Kindel\u00e1n\n|stadium=Av. Plaza Toros\n|location = [[Madrid]], [[Spain|Espa\u00f1a]]\n|attendance=\n|referee=Heredia\n|result=W\n}}\n{{Footballbox collapsible\n|date=19 March 1911\n|time=\n|round = Round 2\n|team1=[[Real Sociedad Gimn\u00e1stica Espa\u00f1ola|RS Gimn\u00e1stica]]\n|score=2\u20130\n|report=\n|team2=Madrid FC\n|goals1=Carruana {{goal}}<br />Espinosa {{goal}}\n|goals2=-\n|stadium=Av. Plaza Toros\n|location = [[Madrid]], [[Spain|Espa\u00f1a]]\n|attendance=\n|referee=Heredia\n|result=L\n}}\n{{Footballbox collapsible\n|date=25 March 1911\n|time=\n|round = Tiebreak Match\n|team1=Madrid FC\n|score=1\u20132\n|report=\n|team2=[[Real Sociedad Gimn\u00e1stica Espa\u00f1ola|RS Gimn\u00e1stica]]\n|goals1=[[Manuel Prats|Prats]] {{goal}}\n|goals2={{goal}} Bourbon<br />{{goal}} Kindel\u00e1n\n|stadium=Av. Plaza Toros\n|location = [[Madrid]], [[Spain|Espa\u00f1a]]\n|attendance=\n|referee=\n|result=L\n}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.realmadrid.com/ Realmadrid.com] Official Site\n*[http://www.leyendablanca.galeon.com/resumen11.htm 1910\u201311 Squad]\n*[http://www.leyendablanca.galeon.com/tempo11.htm 1910\u201311 matches]\n*[http://www.rsssf.com/tabless/span-centrchamp.html#1910-11 1910\u201311 (Campeonato de Madrid)]\n*[http://www.rsssf.com/tablesm/madrid-friend.html International Friendlies of Real Madrid CF \u201