my|title=Testy prok\u00e1zaly dal\u0161\u00ed t\u0159\u00ed p\u0159\u00edpady koronaviru v \u010cesku, celkem je jich osm|website=Mlad\u00e1 fronta DNES|language=cs |date=4 March 2020|access-date=4 March 2020}}</ref>\n| 4 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}}\n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}, [[Auronzo di Cadore]]\n| [[D\u011b\u010d\u00edn]]\n| [[\u00dast\u00ed nad Labem Region]]\n| {{Partial failure|Masaryk Hospital, [[\u00dast\u00ed nad Labem]]}}\n| Male\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | A husband of the infected woman from [[D\u011b\u010d\u00edn]] (case #4).\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''8'''<ref name=\"case7-8\"/>\n| 4 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}}\n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}, [[Auronzo di Cadore]]\n| [[D\u011b\u010d\u00edn]]\n| [[\u00dast\u00ed nad Labem Region]]\n| {{Partial failure|Masaryk Hospital, [[\u00dast\u00ed nad Labem]]}}\n| Female\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | A daughter of the infected woman from [[D\u011b\u010d\u00edn]] (case #4). \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''9'''<ref name=\"case9-12\"/>\n| 5 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}}\n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}, [[Passo del Tonale]]\n| [[Prague]]\n| [[Prague]]\n| {{Success|Home isolation}}\n| Male\n| 45\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | A doctor from Prague who returned from Italy by the end of February. With mild symptoms he continued to examine his patients for two more days. The patient moved from [[Bulovka Hospital]] to home quarantine on 9 March 2020.<ref name=\"mar09.BulovkaRelease\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''10'''<ref name=\"case9-12\"/>\n| 5 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}}\n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}\n| [[Prague]]\n| [[Prague]]\n| {{Success|Home isolation}}\n| M