ag|Italy}}, [[Livigno]]\n| {{n/a}}\n| [[Pilsen Region]]\n| {{n/a}}\n| Female\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | A woman returning from Livigno.<ref name=\"case64\">{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/adamvojtechano/status/1237637984058515463|title=Minister of Health announces case 64|via=Twitter |publisher=AdamVojtechAno|access-date=10 March 2020}}{{Primary source inline}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''65'''\n| 11 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}, [[Trentino]]\n| {{n/a}}\n| [[Zlin Region]]\n| {{n/a}}\n| Male\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{n/a}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | A man was skiing in Trentino.<ref name=\"case65-67\">{{cite web|url=https://www.idnes.cz/brno/zpravy/koronavirus-jizni-morava-jihomoravsky-kraj-brno.A200311_134219_brno-zpravy_mos1|title=Coronavirus first reported by laboratory from Brno, 67 infected in total|website=Mlad\u00e1 fronta DNES|language=cs |access-date=11 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''66'''\n| 11 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}, [[Dolomites]]\n| [[Brno]]\n| [[South Moravian Region]]\n| {{Success|Home isolation}}\n| Male\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | A Man(#66) and a woman(#67) from Brno returned from a skiing holiday in the Dolomites.<ref name=\"case65-67\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''67'''\n| 11 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}, [[Dolomites]]\n| [[Brno]]\n| [[South Moravian Region]]\n| {{Success|Home isolation}}\n| Female\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | A Man(#66) and a woman(#67) from Brno returned from a skiing holiday in the Dolomites.<ref name=\"case65-67\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\