War Novel''. (Phoenix: Key Edition, 2010), {{ISBN|0-615-35379-7}}.\n* Mackinlay, John. ''The Insurgent Archipelago''. (London: Hurst, 2009).\n* [[Mao Zedong]]. ''Aspects of China's Anti-Japanese Struggle'' (1948).\n* Melson, Charles D. \"German Counter-Insurgency Revisited.\" ''Journal of Slavic Military Studies'' 24#1 (2011): 115-146. [http://jmss.org/jmss/index.php/jmss/article/download/442/441 online]\n* Merom, Gil. ''How Democracies Lose Small Wars: State, Society, and the Failures of France in Algeria, Israel in Lebanon, and the United States in Vietnam''. (New York: Cambridge University Press, 2003), {{ISBN|0-521-00877-8}}.\n* [[Robert Grainger Ker Thompson|Thompson, Robert]]. ''Defeating Communist Insurgency: Experiences from Malaya and Vietnam.'' (Chatto & Windus, 1966).\n* Tomes, Robert, [https://web.archive.org/web/20150608194416/http://strategicstudiesinstitute.army.mil/pubs/parameters/Articles/04spring/tomes.pdf \"Relearning Counterinsurgency Warfare\"], ''Parameters'' (Spring 2004) \n* [[Martin van Creveld|Van Creveld, Martin]], ''The Changing Face of War: Combat from the Marne to Iraq'', (New York: Ballantine, 2008). {{ISBN|978-0-89141-902-0}}\n* Zambernardi, Lorenzo. \"Counterinsurgency's Impossible Trilemma\", ''The Washington Quarterly'', Vol. 33, No. 3 (2010), pp.&nbsp;21\u201334.\n* Peter Polack, Guerrilla Warfare; Kings of Revolution, Casemate,{{ISBN|9781612006758}}.\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Counter-insurgency warfare}}\n* [https://www.jstor.org/stable/pdfplus/2010510.pdf?acceptTC=true \"Insurgency: The Transformation of Peasant Rebellion\"] by Raj Desai and Harry Eckstein\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20061218012624/http://www.smallwarsjournal.com/ref/counterinsurgency.htm Small Wars Journal: Insurgency/Counterinsurgency Research page]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20100927074654/http://www.cnas.org/blogs/abumuqawama/2007/10/counterinsurgency-reading-list.html CNAS, Abu Muquwama 'The Counterinsurgency Reading List']\n* [http