ons category|Counter-insurgency warfare}}\n* [https://www.jstor.org/stable/pdfplus/2010510.pdf?acceptTC=true \"Insurgency: The Transformation of Peasant Rebellion\"] by Raj Desai and Harry Eckstein\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20061218012624/http://www.smallwarsjournal.com/ref/counterinsurgency.htm Small Wars Journal: Insurgency/Counterinsurgency Research page]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20100927074654/http://www.cnas.org/blogs/abumuqawama/2007/10/counterinsurgency-reading-list.html CNAS, Abu Muquwama 'The Counterinsurgency Reading List']\n* [http://www.press.umich.edu/titleDetailDesc.do?id=1308805 ''The U.S. Army Stability Operations Field Manual'']\n* [http://studies.agentura.ru/english/listing/terrorismprevention/ Terrorism prevention in Russia: one year after Beslan]\n* [http://earthops.org/sovereign/low_intensity/ \"Military Operations in Low Intensity Conflict\"] U.S. Depts. of the Army and Air Force\n* [http://www.thirdworldtraveler.com/CIA/US_Counterinsurg_Soldier.html \"Inside Counterinsurgency\"] by [[Stan Goff]], ex - U.S. Special Forces\n* [http://www.statecraft.org/ \"Instruments of Statecraft \u2013 U.S. Guerrilla Warfare, Counterinsurgency, and Counterterrorism, 1940\u20131990\"] by Michael McClintock\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20100211083706/http://mass-multi-media.com/CRV \"Counter-Revolutionary Violence \u2013 Bloodbaths in Fact & Propaganda\"] by Noam Chomsky and Edward S. Herman\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20051126102425/http://www.jpfo.org/stroop.htm \"The Warsaw Ghetto Is No More\"] by SS Brigade Commander J\u00fcrgen Stroop\n* [http://www.strategicstudiesinstitute.army.mil/pdffiles/PUB586.pdf \"Insurgency and Counterinsurgency in the 21st Century\"] by Steven Metz and Raymond Millen\n* [https://www.wired.com/news/technology/0,65299-0.html Wired News article on game theory in war on terror]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20070106044249/http://www.jihadmonitor.org/category/military-forces-and-counterterrorism/ Military forces i