017 |work=Ministry of the Interior |language=French}}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n* [[2017 French legislative election]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Mazars, Stephane}}\n[[Category:Year of birth missing (living people)]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Deputies of the 15th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic]]\n[[Category:La R\u00e9publique En Marche politicians]]\n[[Category:Place of birth missing (living people)]]\n[[Category:Senators of Aveyron]]\n\n\n{{France-politician-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Lugnuts", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/St%C3%A9phane_Mazars"}
